My power mum is my mummy!💕💪🏻 Being a new mum to my baby girl, I have a deeper appreciation for my mum’s hard work to bring 4 kids up! I am already very tired with 1 baby, I cannot imagine how my mum managed with 4 of us! 
My mummy’s love for her kids knows no end. Even when I am now a mum myself, my mummy continues to care for me and my baby so unconditionally. 
